name: mahsyar's field
description:
if the sun is a bit away
the vast field has no distance
marching side by side
Shouting and mentioning


"when I took this photo, I was contemplating imagining that at the end of the day we would be walking together in a very wide place."


Taken with Kodak pocket camera with Rollei Retro 400S
location Tumpeng Menoreh, Magelang, Central Java
